comments: Simmons (PHI) cleanly dislodges the ball from Fournier (ORL) on the perimeter.
Possession is correctly awarded to Philadelphia.
Fournier (ORL) holds Simmons (PHI) during the loose ball situation and affects his FOM.
Vucevic (ORL) briefly grasps Embiid's (PHI) elbow but does not prevent him from getting to the loose ball.
Richardson (PHI) is firming up in a screening position in Fournier's (ORL) path when contact occurs and he absorbs the contact.
Horford (PHI) makes contact with Fultz's (ORL) body in transition but Fultz is able to move through the marginal contact.
Horford (PHI) holds Isaac (ORL) during the inbound and affects his FOM.
Simmons (PHI) engages Fultz (ORL) with two hands on ball and affects his SQBR.
Embiid (PHI) and Isaac (ORL) briefly engage and separate during the inbound.
Richardson (PHI) makes incidental "high-five" contact with Vucevic (ORL) after the release on his jump shot attempt.
Simmons (PHI) makes marginal contact with Isaac's (ORL) body before cleanly dislodging the ball.
Simmons (PHI) makes incidental foot contact with the ball after dislodging it in transition.
Embiid (PHI) commits a take foul on Fultz (ORL).
Fournier (ORL) and Harris (PHI) make incidental contact with one another during the rebound.
Simmons (PHI) commits a take foul on Gordon (ORL).  After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the floor of a common foul is confirmed.
Horford (PHI) sets the screen in Fultz's (ORL) path and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Fultz (ORL) makes incidental contact with Richardson's (PHI) arm after the release that does not affect his jump shot attempt.
Horford (PHI) commits a take foul on Fournier (ORL).
Simmons (PHI) sets the pick in Vucevic's (ORL) path and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Horford (PHI) commits a take foul on Fultz (ORL).
Simmons (PHI) does not inbound the ball within five seconds.
Horford (PHI) sets the screen on Fultz (ORL) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Fournier (ORL) makes marginal contact with Harris (PHI) before stealing the inbound pass.
Harris (PHI) commits a take foul on Fournier (ORL).
Vucevic (ORL) gives Embiid (PHI) room to land following his jump shot attempt.
Simmons (PHI) and Fournier (ORL) engage and separate during the inbound.
Simmons (PHI) makes marginal contact with Vucevic's (ORL) body as he intercepts the inbound pass.
Gordon (ORL) legally contests Embiid's (PHI) jump shot attempt.
